WEBVTT

00:04.569 --> 00:06.569
Go!
(inhales deeply)

00:06.571 --> 00:07.303
Come on, Raj!

00:07.305 --> 00:08.204
LEONARD:
You can do this!

00:08.206 --> 00:09.238
There's no way.

00:09.240 --> 00:10.340
What is happening?

00:10.342 --> 00:11.341
This is an Euler's Disk.

00:11.343 --> 00:12.342
It's a physics toy

00:12.344 --> 00:13.810
that demonstrates
angular momentum,

00:13.812 --> 00:15.979
potential energy,
and kinetic energy.

00:15.981 --> 00:18.147
Aw, look at you
watching sports.

00:19.017 --> 00:20.316
We're betting to see
if Koothrappali

00:20.318 --> 00:21.250
can hold his breath

00:21.252 --> 00:22.685
longer than the
disk can spin.

00:22.687 --> 00:24.187
Its weight and smoothness,

00:24.189 --> 00:26.756
along with the slight concavity
of the mirror, means it can spin

00:26.758 --> 00:28.024
for a long time.

00:28.026 --> 00:29.492
But Raj is from India,
which means

00:29.494 --> 00:31.694
he's no slouch
at holding his breath.

00:32.831 --> 00:34.831
Okay, I want in. Ten bucks says
I'll lose interest

00:34.833 --> 00:37.867
before that thing
stops spinning.

00:39.037 --> 00:40.903
Hey, Sheldon, I found a great
restaurant for date night.

00:40.905 --> 00:42.205
Kind of busy right now.

00:42.207 --> 00:44.741
Oh, an Euler's Disk! Fun!
Yeah, we're seeing

00:44.743 --> 00:46.743
if Raj can hold his
breath longer than it.

00:46.745 --> 00:48.711
Oh. Immature.

00:49.681 --> 00:50.880
How ya doing?

00:50.882 --> 00:51.881
Mm.

00:51.883 --> 00:53.216
He's not gonna make it.

00:53.218 --> 00:54.884
Yes, he is!
You know,

00:54.886 --> 00:57.553
deep-sea divers holding
their breath for several minutes

00:57.555 --> 00:59.489
have shown elevated markers
of a protein

00:59.491 --> 01:01.424
that can signal brain damage.

01:01.426 --> 01:04.560
Yeah, see, what's happening here
signals brain damage.

01:05.263 --> 01:06.295
(muffled groaning)

01:06.297 --> 01:07.864
My God, how long does
this thing spin for?

01:07.866 --> 01:11.000
Ha! You're interested!
You're out ten bucks!

01:11.002 --> 01:13.102
It's slowing down!
Dig deep!

01:13.104 --> 01:16.005
Like when we bet you couldn't
fit into Howard's pants!

01:17.776 --> 01:18.508
(groaning)

01:18.510 --> 01:19.542
He's not gonna make it!

01:19.544 --> 01:20.343
Yes, he is!

01:20.345 --> 01:21.644
Come on, Raj!
It's like

01:21.646 --> 01:25.081
your favorite movie!
You're just <i>Waiting to Exhale!</i>

01:28.420 --> 01:29.652
(exhales)

01:29.654 --> 01:31.821
Yeah! I knew you
could do it!

01:32.857 --> 01:34.924
(panting):
And j.. and just so you know,

01:34.926 --> 01:36.759
my favorite movie...

01:36.761 --> 01:39.128
is <i>Princess Bride.</i>

